  "detailed_description": "<h1>UPDATE ROADMAP</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/36ef335ac6954045d9ebc312be83293c.avif?t=1739551205\" width=616 height=1054 /></span></p><br><h1>IMPORTANT NOTICE ABOUT MULTIPLAYER FEATURES</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOCAL MULTIPLAYER</h2>One player can join with a keyboard, but <u>a gamepad is required for additional players to join.</u></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Arcade Party is an exciting co-op party game where 1-4 players can enjoy tons of arcade inspired mini-games together online or locally.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME STAGES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/98f3f51b6c966ceb26415c3de192f80e.poster.avif?t=1739551205\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/98f3f51b6c966ceb26415c3de192f80e.webm?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/98f3f51b6c966ceb26415c3de192f80e.mp4?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Defeat the arcade machines blocking your way by clearing mini-games. Various effects are waiting for each stage.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >20+ VARIETY MINIGAMES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/4f0d25652b3fccb8ec060962e0e9092c.poster.avif?t=1739551205\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/4f0d25652b3fccb8ec060962e0e9092c.webm?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/4f0d25652b3fccb8ec060962e0e9092c.mp4?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play mini-games inspired by classic arcade masterpieces. You will be able to clear the mini-game if you use your various abilities.<br>(The number of minigames is based on Early-Access, and there will be more in the full version)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ONLINE, LOCAL MULTIPLAYER AND SINGLE PLAYER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/8ab13a765f8a364e914f35a74c4aba4a.poster.avif?t=1739551205\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/8ab13a765f8a364e914f35a74c4aba4a.webm?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/8ab13a765f8a364e914f35a74c4aba4a.mp4?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Up to 4 people can play together on one computer (Controller required).  You can also play online if your friends are far away. Also, all mini-games and game modes support single-player.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHARACTER CUSTOMIZATION</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/a82e492854f007d110663a956d66181a.poster.avif?t=1739551205\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/a82e492854f007d110663a956d66181a.webm?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/a82e492854f007d110663a956d66181a.mp4?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>By playing the game and collecting arcade coins, you can customize your character with various costumes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/a78daac0895ebe7a56dd16c692eec073.avif?t=1739551205\" width=600 height=132 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Arcade Party is an exciting co-op party game where 1-4 players can enjoy tons of arcade inspired mini-games together online or locally.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME STAGES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/98f3f51b6c966ceb26415c3de192f80e.poster.avif?t=1739551205\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/98f3f51b6c966ceb26415c3de192f80e.webm?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/98f3f51b6c966ceb26415c3de192f80e.mp4?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Defeat the arcade machines blocking your way by clearing mini-games. Various effects are waiting for each stage.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >20+ VARIETY MINIGAMES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/4f0d25652b3fccb8ec060962e0e9092c.poster.avif?t=1739551205\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/4f0d25652b3fccb8ec060962e0e9092c.webm?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104750/extras/4f0d25652b3fccb8ec060962e0e9092c.mp4?t=1739551205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play mini-games inspired by classic arcade masterpieces. You will be able to clear the mini-game if you use your various abilities.<br>(The number of minigames is based on Early-Access, and there will be more in the full version)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ONLINE, LOCAL MULTIPLAYER AND SINGLE PLAYER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline p